Package: nmr.spectra.processing
Title: Process Fourier-transformed NMR spectra
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("AndrÃ©s", "Bernal", , "AndresFernando.BernalEscobar@murdoch.edu.au", 
            role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1668-7225"))
Description: Collection of tools for processing Fourier-transformed NMR spectra:
 baseline correction, shifting, alignment, calibration to a reference resonance, 
 peak integration and more. Also packs some utils to help navigate NMR data without 
 leaving R.
